[2020-08-11 08:31:22.000000 192.130.74.18  - [query->NORTIZ] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='8/11/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago

, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta

[2020-08-11 10:12:45.000000 192.130.74.18  - [query->NORTIZ] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='8/11/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, max(c.initials) usuario

, max(c.initials), ' '

, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta

[2020-08-11 11:52:44.000000 192.130.74.30  - [query->CRIVERA] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='8/11/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac

, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago

, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta

, max(b.statfact) statfact
